WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:06:34.159
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:45.519
Darkness is trying to set in Mystery Babylon. I'm telling you, great Mystery Babylon. It will be like a dark blanket will blanket thee.

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:51.919
If they choose this man (Zohran Mamdani), I see a dark blanket blanketing, and people will flee.

00:06:51.920 --> 00:07:02.719
I hear the word flee. They will leave by the tens of thousands, if not hundreds of thousands.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:12.167
They will leave. People, I see them fleeing if he's voted in. People will know that this is the end.

00:07:12.168 --> 00:07:20.159
Father, you know if he'll be voted in or not; what I'm hearing you say is what I'm seeing is going to happen.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:29.399
He said, "No, they still have a choice. They have a choice to vote."He's held a veil.

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:39.079
I don't see the outcome, but I see the outcome if they vote this way concerning this man.

00:07:39.080 --> 00:07:47.097
I see a dark cloud; it's a dark blanket over them. And I see financial structures falling.

00:07:47.098 --> 00:07:53.818
I see the financial institutions and all the money falling.

00:07:53.819 --> 00:08:19.400
I see a fleeing of the city, like people saying, "We're out of here!"I see it's like a mass migration of people coming. People fleeing certain areas.

